room_title: Escape room "Bloody Mary" by Room Raiders in West Palm Beach
room_address: 7104 S Military Trail, Lake Worth, FL 33463
room_description: Legend has it that Bloody Mary for centuries has wreaked havoc across the world, leaving mayhem behind. With no one being safe, no one knows where or when she may strike next. Her victim count keeps rising. Do you and your team have what it takes to vanquish Bloody Mary once and for all by entering her manor where it all began? You have one hour before she comes for you and traps your soul inside her manor for eternal torture. Vanquish Bloody Mary or perish with the rest.
